              <line x1="25" y1="13" x2="38" y2="33" stroke="#1e3a5f" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="35" x2="38" y2="35" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="logo-text">
            <span class="brand-name">Cosmos Web Tech</span>
            <span class="brand-tagline">Your Digital Universe</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services" class="active">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/demos">Demos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/resources">Resources</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-small">Get Quote</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="mobile-menu-btn" aria-label="Toggle menu">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/services">Services</a> / <span>Hosting & Maintenance</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>Website Hosting & Maintenance</h1>
      <p>Keep your website secure, fast, and always online</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-detail">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-main">
          <h2>Peace of Mind for Your Website</h2>
          <p>Your website is a critical business asset. Downtime means lost customers and revenue. Security breaches can destroy your reputation. Our managed hosting and maintenance services ensure your website is always secure, fast, and available.</p>

          <p>We handle all the technical details so you can focus on running your business. From daily backups to security updates, we've got you covered.</p>

          <h3>What's Included</h3>

          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                  <rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                  <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/>
                  <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Fast Australian Hosting</h4>
              <p>Servers located in Sydney for the fastest possible load times for Australian visitors.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
                  <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/>
                  <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Daily Backups</h4>
              <p>Automatic daily backups stored securely. Restore your site in minutes if anything goes wrong.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Security Monitoring</h4>
              <p>24/7 malware scanning and intrusion detection. We catch threats before they cause damage.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                  <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>SSL Certificate</h4>
              <p>Free SSL certificate included. Your site displays the secure padlock in browsers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                  <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Uptime Monitoring</h4>
              <p>We monitor your site 24/7 and get alerted instantly if it goes down.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Regular Updates</h4>
              <p>WordPress core, theme, and plugin updates applied regularly to keep your site secure.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Why Managed Hosting?</h3>
          <p>Cheap shared hosting might seem like a bargain, but it comes with hidden costs:</p>

          <div class="comparison-boxes">
            <div class="comparison-box bad">
              <h4>Cheap Shared Hosting</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Slow load times</li>
                <li>No backups (or you do them)</li>
                <li>Security is your problem</li>
                <li>Shared with 1000s of sites</li>
                <li>Support via ticket only</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="comparison-box good">
              <h4>Our Managed Hosting</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Fast Australian servers</li>
                <li>Daily automatic backups</li>
                <li>Security monitoring included</li>
                <li>Isolated environment</li>
                <li>Direct phone support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Maintenance Services</h3>
          <p>Beyond hosting, we offer ongoing maintenance to keep your website in top shape:</p>

          <ul class="check-list">
            <li><strong>Content Updates</strong> - Text, images, and minor changes</li>
            <li><strong>Plugin Updates</strong> - Keep everything current and secure</li>
            <li><strong>Performance Monitoring</strong> - Ensure fast load times</li>
            <li><strong>Security Patches</strong> - Immediate response to vulnerabilities</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Support</strong> - Help when you need it</li>
            <li><strong>Monthly Reports</strong> - See what we've done for you</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Hosting & Maintenance Plans</h3>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>Basic</h4>
              <div class="package-price">$50/mo</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Fast Australian hosting</li>
                <li>SSL certificate</li>
                <li>Daily backups</li>
                <li>Monthly updates</li>
                <li>Email support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="package featured">
              <span class="package-badge">Most Popular</span>
              <h4>Standard</h4>
              <div class="package-price">$100/mo</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Everything in Basic</li>
                <li>Weekly updates</li>
                <li>2 hours content updates</li>
                <li>Priority support</li>
                <li>Uptime monitoring</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>Premium</h4>
              <div class="package-price">$200/mo</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Everything in Standard</li>
                <li>5 hours maintenance</li>
                <li>Same-day response</li>
                <li>Performance optimization</li>
                <li>Monthly reporting</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <a href="/contact?service=hosting" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" style="width: 100%;">Get Started</a>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Already Hosted Elsewhere?</h3>
            <p class="sidebar-text">We can manage your site wherever it's hosted, or migrate it to our servers for free.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="sidebar-link">Contact us to discuss →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta section-navy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready for Hassle-Free Hosting?</h2>
        <p>Get peace of mind with managed hosting and maintenance.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-large">Get Started</a>
          <a href="tel:0433309677" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-large">Call 0433 309 677</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="logo footer-logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 50 50" fill="none"><circle cx="25" cy="10" r="3" fill="#ffffff"/><circle cx="10" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3b82f6"/><circle cx="40" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3b82f6"/><line x1="25" y1="13" x2="12" y2="33" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="25" y1="13" x2="38" y2="33" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="12" y1="35" x2="38" y2="35" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-text">
              <span class="brand-name" style="color: white;">Cosmos Web Tech</span>
              <span class="brand-tagline">Your Digital Universe</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Services</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="/services/web-design">Web Design</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/wordpress">WordPress</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/ecommerce">E-commerce</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/odoo">Odoo</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/seo">SEO Services</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Company</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/demos">Demos</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Contact</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li>Bella Vista, NSW 2153</li>
            <li><a href="tel:0433309677">0433 309 677</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Cosmos Web Tech. ABN: 32 164 690 751. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 100%);
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .breadcrumb { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--grey-300); }
  .breadcrumb span { color: var(--grey-light); }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: var(--grey-300); font-size: 1.25rem; }

  .service-detail { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .service-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px; gap: 3rem; }
  .service-main h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-main h3 { margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-main p { color: var(--grey-dark); line-height: 1.8; }

  .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .feature-item { padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--grey-100); border-radius: 12px; }
  .feature-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: var(--white); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .feature-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; stroke: var(--accent); }
  .feature-item h4 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .feature-item p { font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; color: var(--grey); }

  .comparison-boxes { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .comparison-box { padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; }
  .comparison-box.bad { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
  .comparison-box.good { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
  .comparison-box h4 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .comparison-box ul { list-style: none; }
  .comparison-box li { padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .comparison-box.bad li::before { content: '✗'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--error); }
  .comparison-box.good li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--success); }

  .check-list { list-style: none; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .check-list li { padding: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-200); }
  .check-list li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--success); font-weight: bold; }

  .sidebar-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--grey-200); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .sidebar-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .sidebar-text { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--grey); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .sidebar-link { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

  .package { padding: 1.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-200); position: relative; }
  .package:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .package.featured { background: var(--grey-100); margin: 0 -2rem; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; }
  .package-badge { position: absolute; top: 0.5rem; right: 0.5rem; background: var(--accent); color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .package h4 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .package-price { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .package ul { list-style: none; }
  .package li { padding: 0.25rem 0 0.25rem 1.25rem; position: relative; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--grey-dark); }
  .package li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--success); }

  .cta { padding: 5rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .cta h2 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta p { color: var(--grey-300); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; }
  .btn-outline-white { background: transparent; color: var(--white); border: 2px solid var(--white); }
  .btn-outline-white:hover { background: var(--white); color: var(--navy-dark); }
  .nav-links a.active { color: var(--accent); }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .service-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid, .comparison-boxes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  }
</style>
